<![CDATA[<font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Hi there&nbsp;{!Account.FirstName},</span></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I hope you and your family had a great &nbsp;summer on your new boat! Hopefully you haven't had reason to bring your motor in to be serviced because I noticed that you didn't take the Extended Warranty on your Mercury motor when you took ownership of your boat. &nbsp;&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">I know we've already discussed the Extended Warranty when you purchased your boat, but I just wanted to reiterate that the investment in Extended Warranty is often less than the cost of the first major repair that would be covered under warranty. For a short window of time I can still qualify you for the original Extended Warranty rates as discussed.&nbsp;</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">I would like to give you another opportunity to protect your new Mercury engine and consider the Extended Warranty again.&nbsp;</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Thank you again for being a valued member of the Legend Family, please feel free to call me if you have any questions and, of course, if you would like to take advantage of this offer!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Yours in Boating,</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div><font face="arial">{!User.Name}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Business Office Manager</div>]]></td>
